# Next.js Casing Standards

- Component files should use lowercase with dashes (e.g., `header.tsx`, `dropdown-menu.tsx`)
- Variables, functions, and hooks should use camel case (e.g., `useAuth`, `getUserById`)
- Use lowercase with dashes for directories (e.g., `components/auth-wizard`)